  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The power cut time is also long",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the lack of sufficient fuels and water to generate electricity, the power cut will last for three hours.",
        "It has been announced that this procedure will be in force from tomorrow (27) to July 3."
      ],
